---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About — Helen's Home Care"
  description="Helen's Home Care LLC is a family-owned, Texas-licensed personal assistance services agency serving the Dallas–Fort Worth area."
>
  <section class="bg-mist/40">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-16 md:py-20">
      <div class="roofline" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <h1 class="mt-6 font-display text-4xl text-navy md:text-5xl">About Helen's Home Care</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-16">
    <img
      src="/images/care-groceries.jpg"
      alt="A Helen's Home Care caregiver bringing groceries to an older man at home"
      width="1600"
      height="1061"
      class="mb-14 h-64 w-full rounded-xl object-cover shadow-sm md:h-[420px]"
      loading="eager"
    />
    <div class="grid gap-14 md:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr]">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate">
        <p>
          Helen's Home Care is a family-owned personal assistance services
          agency based in Dallas, Texas. We started with a simple conviction:
          growing older shouldn't mean leaving home, and families shouldn't
          have to carry the weight of daily care alone.
        </p>
        <p>
          We're licensed by the Texas Health and Human Services Commission as
          a Home and Community Support Services Agency providing Personal
          Assistance Services — the state's licensing category for the
          non-medical support we deliver: personal care, meals, companionship,
          errands, and household help.
        </p>
        <p>
          What makes care good isn't complicated. It's the same caregiver
          showing up on time, week after week. It's noticing that Dad seems
          quieter than usual and telling the family. It's treating someone's
          home, routine, and preferences with respect. That's the standard we
          hold ourselves to.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="space-y-8">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-mist bg-white p-7 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-sky">Leadership</h2>
          <dl class="mt-4 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <dt class="font-semibold text-navy">Alex Maouene</dt>
              <dd class="text-base text-slate">Owner &amp; Administrator</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt class="font-semibold text-navy">Monteca Oleko</dt>
              <dd class="text-base text-slate">Alternate Administrator</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-mist bg-white p-7 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-sky">Service area</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate">
            Dallas and surrounding communities in the Dallas–Fort Worth
            metroplex. Not sure if you're in our area? Call us — if we can't
            serve you, we'll help you find someone who can.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-mist bg-white p-7 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-sky">Our caregivers</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate">
            Every caregiver is screened, background-checked, trained, and
            employed by us — never subcontracted. We match caregivers to
            clients by needs and personality, and we keep the match consistent.
          </p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 rounded-xl bg-navy px-8 py-12 text-center md:px-16">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-white">Meet us before you decide</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-mist/90">
        The free in-home visit is as much for you to interview us as it is for
        us to understand your family.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-white px-6 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-navy transition-colors hover:bg-mist"
      >
        Schedule a visit
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
